title: 679: BITCOIN WILL SKYROCKET ANOTHER 10X - HERE’S WHEN, ACCORDING TO STOCK-TO-FLOW MODEL CREATOR!!!!!
description:
The pseudo-anonymous Bitcoin analyst called Plan B gave his 704,000 Twitter followers an update on the stock-to-flow (S2F) BTC price model.

Plan B stressed on August 27, that the “next months will be key” as he believes the Bitcoin S2F model predicts a minimal $100K by Christmas and also predicts, Bitcoin continues its 10+ year path and does another 10x in 4 years."
